title: North West Dresses Up as the Tooth Fairy in Kim Kardashian's Adorable Video
text:
‘KUWTK’ Season 13 Trailer: Scott Disick Says He’s a Sex Addict 
Moments before North played dress-up, Kardashian told her Snapchat followers that she didn't get much sleep the night before because she presented an award to KUWTK executive producer Jonathan Murray at the Family Equality Council's Impact Awards gala in Los Angeles. 
"You guys, I'm, like, so tired. My kids got up so early," the reality star, who is also mom of 15-month-old son Saint with husband Kanye West , said while rubbing her eyes and relaxing in bed. "Does anyone know the feeling? I want them to sleep in on a Sunday." 14 Times Kim Kardashian Was Actually Funny 
In a follow-up video, Kardashian playfully told a bunny-filtered North, "Please, go back to sleep. You've been up for three hours." After North pretended to cry, her mom laughed and cuddled with her in bed.
